# Match game-is-up: keep build context small and reproducible.
# Never copy real env files into the build context (they hold secrets, and the
# build is env-independent — db:generate uses a placeholder). Keep the templates.
.env
.env.*
!.env*.example
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/.cache
.git
.github
.devcontainer
.husky
.vscode
**/coverage
data
!data/demo-library
!data/demo-library/**
!data/demo-camera-snapshots
!data/demo-camera-snapshots/**
!data/demo-captures
!data/demo-captures/**
apps/api/data
apps/bridge/release
!apps/web/src/data
!apps/web/src/data/**
apps/web/public/README.md
deploy
*.log
tmp
